overview.en: The Online Game Application Chain global game ecosystem is based on blockchain technology that seamlessly integrates blockchain and games, enabling eco-integration of Token, blockchain and gaming industries.
overview.zh: Online Game Application Chain全球游戏生态系统基于区块链技术实现了区块链和游戏的无缝融合，实现了Token、区块链和游戏产业的生态融合。
